thread.title_full: LymphedemaProducts.com reviewed by David C Hoover

author: David C Hoover
title: David C Hoover
text:
Service was good. Length of time to receive the order was as posted on order but I had to pay the price for priority mail in order to get the order by the time the therapist needed it.
I will order from Lymphedema Products again.
